{
  "stem": "11175.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was in the [INAUDIBLE], and we looked up and the buildings we saw the fires.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We saw-- and I saw a red flag, the-- the blue-white flag on the-- on a roof, you know, and the building was on fire.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You couldn't get out from it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and-- and to come in here, to come into the [INAUDIBLE] and take out the people, they couldn't take out the people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were there--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then finally came an order we should come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're going to make a selection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We have to go over to the [INAUDIBLE] to the military prison that was corner of [INAUDIBLE] and Simonhof.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was-- we came up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was the whole-- the whole-- elite from the SS.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Brandt ?] was there and Konrad was there and some other SS leaders, you know, were there standing and we were together and there were a thousand-- more than a thousand people, you know?",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And as we were standing there, they brought over from the camp, two SS men brought over a kapo, a man with a girl, and they were carrying a-- a basket in their hand.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In the basket, it was-- the bottles with the cocktail-- Molotov cocktails.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there used to be on that corner from the [INAUDIBLE], because I knew it, a toilet during the day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know you going during the day, the people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was the-- the the SS man took out one bottle from the-- from the basket, and he throwed it at the wall and it exploded.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were there about two hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then there came an order we should go back to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went back to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
